1
00:00:07,460 --> 00:00:10,180
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:14,140
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,820
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:19,820
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:24,700
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:30,820
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:34,660
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:39,340
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:43,660
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:50,060
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,620 --> 00:00:54,220
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:57,940
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:04,900
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,700
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:16,700
=Episode 21=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,500
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk Launch)
Yes!

18
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:22,300
30 taels for one piece?

19
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:23,500
That does sound a little steep.

20
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,300
But just like Xianquan Tavern,

21
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:29,700
we champion high quality at low prices,

22
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:31,820
staying true
to a people-first philosophy.

23
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:35,500
Today, right here at Xianquan Tavern,

24
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:38,420
the Gambiered Silk
won't cost you 30 taels,

25
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:40,500
not even 20 taels.

26
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:44,700
Just 19.9 taels.

27
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:47,900
We want to succeed again

28
00:01:48,380 --> 00:01:50,700
and let the love of the common people

29
00:01:50,980 --> 00:01:53,700
change this world!

30
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:54,620
Bravo!

31
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:56,100
- Bravo!
- Yeah!

32
00:01:56,540 --> 00:01:58,100
- Amazing!
- Only 19.9 taels!

33
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,980
For Feng City,

34
00:01:58,980 --> 00:01:59,900
I'll take one

35
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:00,700
of the new Gambiered Silk!

36
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:03,100
Let's get Gambiered Silk
back as a royal tribute!

37
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:04,740
Every Feng City citizen
has a duty to help!

38
00:02:04,820 --> 00:02:06,180
I'll support it too!

39
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:07,060
Me too!

40
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,500
I'll take ten!

41
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:12,860
- Taking ten at once?
- Ten at once?

42
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:13,820
Sorry, sir,

43
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:14,620
you can't do that.

44
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:17,180
It's limited to one piece per person.

45
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:19,700
Besides, production of Gambiered Silk
is limited.

46
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,580
You'll need to place a deposit first.

47
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:24,940
Alright.

48
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:26,100
One it is, then.

49
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,300
I'll pay the deposit first.

50
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:28,540
I'll pay the deposit.

51
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:30,020
Don't be fooled by him!

52
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,580
He's Li Yunhe, the live-in son-in-law

53
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:32,300
from the Zhou household.

54
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:33,940
I know who he is.

55
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:35,300
He's just a shill!

56
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:37,300
- A shill?
- The Zhou live-in son-in-law?

57
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:37,740
I...

58
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:38,620
No, wait.

59
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:39,500
Everyone, calm down.

60
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,140
I...

61
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:41,600
Only 19.9 taels?

62
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:42,500
If you don't want it, I do!

63
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,260
I want it!

64
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:45,580
Me too! Me too!

65
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:46,940
Hold on!

66
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:50,380
Mr. Li?

67
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:52,020
Mr. Li,

68
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,380
we met at Chunfeng Pavilion.

69
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,220
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk

70
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:56,500
is fantastic!

71
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:58,500
My friends, merchant envoys
from the tributary states,

72
00:02:58,500 --> 00:02:59,060
thank you so much

73
00:02:59,060 --> 00:03:01,100
for your appreciation
of our Gambiered Silk.

74
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:03,180
However, if you wish to purchase it,

75
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:05,300
the price is not 19.9 taels.

76
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:06,900
It's 39.9 taels.

77
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:08,100
What's the meaning of this?

78
00:03:08,220 --> 00:03:09,780
This is blatant discrimination!

79
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:12,140
We're truly grateful
you like our Gambiered Silk,

80
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:14,940
but this special promotion
at Xianquan Tavern

81
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,500
is exclusively
for the citizens of Daqian.

82
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,300
Why is that?

83
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:20,900
The prosperity Daqian enjoys today,

84
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:22,900
the peace we have here in Feng City,

85
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,740
what do we owe it all to?

86
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:25,940
It all rests on the shoulders
of Daqian's own people.

87
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:27,740
That's why this special discount today

88
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:30,020
goes entirely to the people of Daqian.

89
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:32,340
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

90
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:34,100
Mr. Li speaks the truth!

91
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,700
Daqian is the nation of all its people!

92
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:38,540
I'll take this new Gambiered Silk!

93
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,180
How much for the deposit?
I'll pay right now!

94
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,620
Taking payment, right? Here.

95
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:44,500
I want it!

96
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,380
Hey, wait.

97
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,060
No rush.

98
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:46,900
Get in line.

99
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:50,060
- I'll take some too!
- Me too!

100
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:52,180
Line up now!

101
00:03:52,180 --> 00:03:53,180
There's plenty for everyone!

102
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:54,420
I want one too!

103
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:55,300
Ten taels?

104
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,100
Li Yunhe,

105
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,020
you haven't even delivered
the actual clothes yet.

106
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:02,380
How on earth did you get them to
fork over their money?

107
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:03,780
What do you know?

108
00:04:04,020 --> 00:04:05,900
Good wine needs no bush.

109
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:06,860
A truly good product

110
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:09,060
will naturally be sought after
by the masses.

111
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,500
And another thing.

112
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:12,060
Don't tell me you thought

113
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:13,260
this whole Gambiered Silk extravaganza

114
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:14,180
didn't cost any money?

115
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:15,060
So

116
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:17,980
the key to getting Gambiered Silk
back as a royal tribute

117
00:04:18,140 --> 00:04:21,340
lies in the grand super-show
three days from now?

118
00:04:21,340 --> 00:04:22,420
Grand secrets must not be revealed.

119
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:25,100
Are you really going to sell
to those foreign merchants

120
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:27,180
for 39.9 taels a piece?

121
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:28,180
Obviously.

122
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:30,500
You think Feng City's infrastructure
was built for free?

123
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,380
You think the thriving business
environment Daqian provides

124
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:33,180
costs nothing?

125
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,740
Charge them a bit extra,

126
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:35,500
and we'll have

127
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,580
more tax silver
to hand over to the imperial court.

128
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,100
As merchants,

129
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:41,420
shouldn't we have
at least a little patriotism?

130
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:42,820
I never would have guessed

131
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:45,300
a guy like you, who seems obsessed
with nothing but money,

132
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,900
would actually care so much
about the nation.

133
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:50,180
Fine. We'll do it your way.

134
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,580
I'm curious to see

135
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,100
how you plan to turn the tide.

136
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:56,220
What's the rush?

137
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,700
This is only the first layer of my plan.

138
00:04:58,900 --> 00:04:59,980
The real show

139
00:05:01,100 --> 00:05:01,940
is yet to come.

140
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:40,780
Prince Ning,

141
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:42,180
please, have some tea.

142
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:44,380
What's that crowd across the way
at Xianquan Tavern

143
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:45,900
scrambling over?

144
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:49,900
Clearly, it's that country bumpkin,

145
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:50,900
Li Yunhe,

146
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:51,780
pulling another one of his cheap tricks

147
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,500
to swindle the gullible masses.

148
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:54,460
But

149
00:05:54,580 --> 00:05:56,100
he won't be bouncing around much longer.

150
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,660
Li Yunhe?

151
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:01,020
Is he the great talent
who wrote the lines,

152
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:03,540
"Heaven gave me talents,
destined for a grand design.

153
00:06:03,540 --> 00:06:05,900
A fortune squandered?
It will all come back in time"?

154
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:07,860
That poet?

155
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:09,540
That's the one.

156
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:15,220
He truly does possess talent.

157
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:18,380
If I could recruit him under my banner
and put him to good use,

158
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:20,780
someday it might even
be remembered as a legendary tale

159
00:06:20,780 --> 00:06:23,140
of a fine judge of talent
discovering a hidden gem.

160
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:25,100
Your Highness,
you mustn't be so quick to believe

161
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:26,620
those common street rumors.

162
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,060
Li Yunhe

163
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,820
is nothing but a live-in son-in-law
at the Zhou Manor.

164
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:31,220
He has no real ability to speak of,

165
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:33,100
but he sure knows
how to swindle the ignorant masses

166
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,300
out of their money.

167
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,980
Marquis of Zhennan,

168
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:39,980
your son certainly has a sharp wit.

169
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:41,740
- Haha.
- Haha.

170
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:43,620
Before I arrived in Feng City,

171
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:45,020
I'd already heard

172
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:48,020
that Feng City was ravaged by floods,

173
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:50,020
the displaced refugees
multiplying by the day.

174
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:53,900
Grain prices within the city
were soaring out of control,

175
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:56,100
and the Prefect was at his wits' end.

176
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:58,620
Then Li Yunhe laid out
a strategy that settled everything.

177
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:01,500
In just three days,
he stabilized Feng City's grain prices

178
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:03,620
and brought them back to normal.

179
00:07:03,980 --> 00:07:05,140
Right on the heels of that,

180
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:07,420
at the Chunfeng Pavilion
poetry gathering,

181
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:09,500
he delivered three timeless masterpieces
in a single breath,

182
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:10,980
stealing the entire spotlight.

183
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:14,180
He stands out as a great talent,

184
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:16,700
a man of both brilliant literary genius
and capable statecraft.

185
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:22,820
Marquis of Zhennan,

186
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:24,740
could it be that you're worried
about your own standing

187
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:27,220
and don't want a man
of such ability to serve me?

188
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:28,580
So you put your heir

189
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:30,380
to run him down and paint him
as worthless?

190
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,620
Could that be it?

191
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:32,460
Haha.

192
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:33,140
Of course not.

193
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:33,900
Haha.

194
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,420
Prince Ning, you jest.

195
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,500
He is merely a live-in son-in-law

196
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,940
of the insignificant Zhou family,

197
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:42,900
without a single official title
to his name.

198
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,220
To earn Your Highness's esteemed favor,

199
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:46,260
that would be the greatest honor

200
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,980
he could ever have.

201
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:51,740
Attendants!

202
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:56,780
Go to my residence at once
and fetch 1,000 taels of gold.

203
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:58,580
Deliver it to the Zhou Manor

204
00:07:58,580 --> 00:07:59,900
for Li Yunhe.

205
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:03,100
Tell him I admire his talent

206
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,740
and invite him to my residence
for a conversation.

207
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:07,420
What are you gawking at?

208
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,220
Get moving!

209
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:13,620
Marquis of Zhennan, for you to hold
firm in Feng City for so many years,

210
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:16,940
you're indeed a man of great insight.

211
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:17,940
Prince Ning, you flatter me.

212
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,140
Leave us.

213
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,660
Prince Ning,

214
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:36,620
now that everyone in this room
is one of our own,

215
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,500
may I ask,

216
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:46,300
how are your preparations going?

217
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:49,380
Everything is in place.

218
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:51,980
We're just waiting for the right moment.

219
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,500
Marquis of Zhennan,

220
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,260
I've heard that quite a stockpile

221
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:57,980
of grain and fodder
has been hoarded here in Feng City.

222
00:08:58,380 --> 00:08:59,180
Is that true?

223
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:00,780
Absolutely true.

224
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:04,300
All those shenanigans of Li Yunhe's

225
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:06,380
left many merchants in Feng City

226
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:08,780
sitting on massive stockpiles
of overpriced grain,

227
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:09,740
unable to sell it off.

228
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:13,500
And on top of that, the imperial court's
disaster relief grain

229
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:14,980
has already arrived.

230
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:18,980
Even heaven is on my side.

231
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,700
With plentiful grain and fodder,

232
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:22,500
once I retrieve
the late emperor's edict,

233
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,940
I can march the army north

234
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,340
and strike down the pretender.

235
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,980
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

236
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:31,100
May victory unfurl
at the first blow of your banner,

237
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:32,540
and may you reclaim the sacred throne.

238
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:37,220
Once I have accomplished
this great task,

239
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:39,260
your hereditary title

240
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:40,100
of Marquis of Zhennan

241
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,820
should be elevated to the next rank.

242
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,780
Isn't that right,

243
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:45,980
Prince of Zhennan?

244
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,420
Thank you, Your Majesty.

245
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:58,540
(Zhou Manor)

246
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:14,980
What the...

247
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,780
Where did you pop out from?

248
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:17,420
Mr. Li,

249
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:19,380
today, the Marquis House sent men
with a message.

250
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:21,980
They wish to invite you over
for a conversation.

251
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,380
The Marquis House?

252
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:24,580
Yes.

253
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:26,220
They said to invite you over for a chat,

254
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:28,220
and they brought 1,000 taels of gold.

255
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,380
1,000 taels of gold?

256
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:33,420
Yes.

257
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:34,340
Come on,

258
00:10:34,420 --> 00:10:35,620
bring the gold in.

259
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:46,620
(One Thousand Taels of Gold)

260
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:50,500
Is the Marquis House trying to be funny?

261
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,180
An empty promise
scrawled on a blank note.

262
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,980
Didn't they bring any verbal message?

263
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:56,980
There's nothing else.

264
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,620
Just a blank slip of paper like this,

265
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:03,980
and they expect me
to walk right to my death?

266
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:05,300
From the looks of it,

267
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:07,860
this wasn't Lu Qifeng's handiwork.

268
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:09,980
Could it be

269
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:12,780
that old fox from the Marquis House
has returned?

270
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:13,900
Word has it

271
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:14,580
the Marquis of Zhennan

272
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:16,060
has indeed come back to the manor.

273
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,980
That old fox sure knows
how to pick his moment.

274
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,020
He just has to rush back

275
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,380
right at this exact moment.

276
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:27,500
And the second he's back,
he summons me for a little chat.

277
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:30,380
Alright.

278
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:31,660
If there's nothing else,

279
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:33,020
back to work.

280
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,980
Understood. I take my leave.

281
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,020
Bad news, my lady.

282
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,500
What's happened?

283
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:58,020
My lady,

284
00:11:58,020 --> 00:11:59,260
Mr. Li is packing his things.

285
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,380
It looks like he's about
to leave the Zhou Manor.

286
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:09,060
Li Yunhe!

287
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:14,980
What are you doing?

288
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,020
These are critical times right now.

289
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:20,380
I need to go hold the fort
at Xianquan Tavern.

290
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:23,660
If you're just going to hold the fort
at Xianquan Tavern,

291
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:25,060
do you really need to pack up

292
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:26,900
every last thing you own?

293
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:30,420
You're worried you'll drag

294
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,780
the Zhou family down with you,
aren't you?

295
00:12:41,220 --> 00:12:42,300
Sometimes,

296
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,980
you're so smart that it's infuriating.

297
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:47,700
♪See the silk blanket the long hallway♪

298
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:48,940
That's right.

299
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:51,220
What I'm about to do next

300
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:53,580
won't just offend
the Marquis of Zhennan.

301
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,220
It might even
make an enemy of Prince Ning.

302
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,660
If I stay here in the Zhou Manor,

303
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:01,260
disaster is bound to follow me here.

304
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,420
But don't forget,

305
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:05,300
by now, everyone knows

306
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:08,220
the Zhou family has already
taken a stand by your side.

307
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:09,420
Yu.

308
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,260
The situation has changed.

309
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:14,060
The Marquis of Zhennan
has returned to Feng City,

310
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:16,860
and Prince Ning
has surely arrived as well.

311
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:20,260
The time we have left

312
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,780
is far too tight.

313
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:23,340
I don't have the time
to run back and forth.

314
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:26,180
But without my family's protection,

315
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,060
you'll be in even greater danger.

316
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,380
Fortune favors the bold.

317
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,820
Once I leave the Zhou Manor,

318
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,660
they'll shift all their focus

319
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:39,860
right onto Xianquan Tavern.

320
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,260
Even if they all turn on me at once,

321
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:44,660
it'll buy the Zhou family enough time.

322
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:46,860
Li Yunhe.

323
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,860
I'm so worried about you.

324
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:55,500
Yu,

325
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,100
promise me.

326
00:13:57,580 --> 00:13:58,980
You have to keep yourself safe.

327
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:01,980
If danger comes, hide.

328
00:14:03,180 --> 00:14:04,180
I will definitely come and find you.

329
00:14:09,140 --> 00:14:12,820
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

330
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:16,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

331
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:22,380
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

332
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:23,380
Li Yunhe.

333
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:25,860
What's wrong?

334
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,580
Take good care of yourself.

335
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:36,540
I will.

336
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:42,260
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

337
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:43,700
(Yu,)

338
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,900
(if I never return,)

339
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,700
(then just forget I was never here.)

340
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:56,300
(Li Yunhe,)

341
00:14:57,380 --> 00:14:58,660
(I will wait for you to come back.)

342
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:02,180
(I will definitely wait for you
to come back.)

343
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:40,060
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

344
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:43,420
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

345
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:46,660
♪Who took the March rain♪

346
00:15:46,900 --> 00:15:50,260
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

347
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:53,420
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

348
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:56,780
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

349
00:15:57,660 --> 00:16:03,580
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

350
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:07,060
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

351
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:10,140
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

352
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:12,580
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

353
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:16,780
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

354
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:20,140
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

355
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:23,420
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

356
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:26,860
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

357
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:33,540
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

358
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:03,340
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

359
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:06,740
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

360
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:10,060
♪Who took the March rain♪

361
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:13,580
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

362
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:16,860
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

363
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:20,660
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

364
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:23,980
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

365
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:26,940
♪As seasons change♪

366
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:30,580
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

367
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:33,420
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

368
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:36,060
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

369
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:40,140
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

370
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:43,460
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

371
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:47,180
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

372
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:50,700
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

373
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:53,580
♪Only for you♪

374
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:57,180
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

375
00:17:57,300 --> 00:18:00,060
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

376
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:02,740
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

377
00:18:02,740 --> 00:18:06,820
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

378
00:18:06,820 --> 00:18:10,140
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

379
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:13,540
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

380
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:20,060
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

381
00:18:21,140 --> 00:18:25,260
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

382
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:31,060
♪Your wedding gown♪
